---
title: Now page
description: A timeline of what going on in my life. I try to check in every month or so.
about: |
  ## About now pages

  Now pages are sort of like a chronological social media feed but with fewer updates. Check out [this explainer](https://nownownow.com/about) for a, well, explainer.
layout: layouts/page.njk
bodyClass: now
---
<ol class="timeline" role="list">
  {% for post in collections.now | reverse %}
    <li>
      <article class="timeline-teaser flow">
        <h2 class="timeline-teaser__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        {% if post.data.excerpt %}
        {% set excerptContent %}{{ post.data.excerpt }}{% endset %}
        {{ excerptContent | markdownify | safe }}
        {% else %}
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <a class="cta cta--primary" href="{{ post.url }}">Full post â†’</a>
      </article>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ol>